title: UAE: Emirates named 2025 Best International Airline, wins multiple global awards
description: Emirates has been named Best International Airline for the second consecutive year, receiving multiple awards for its First Class and lounge services. The airline also won Best Long-Haul Airline and Middle East’s Leading Airline Brand. Recognized for its cabin crew, private suites, and network expansion to five new destinations, Emirates continues to lead in global air travel.
